'''''Peer Review''''' is a quarterly [[magazine]] published by the [[Association of American Colleges and Universities]] that reports "emerging trends and key debates in undergraduate liberal education". It was established in early 2000 and the [[editor-in-chief]] is Shelley Johnson Carey.<ref name=aac>{{cite web|title=About Peer Review|url=https://www.aacu.org/peerreview/about|publisher=Association of American Colleges and Universities|accessdate=14 December 2015}}</ref> The magazine is based in [[Washington DC]].<ref name=aac/>

